      <title>中国国会承诺要解决钢铁和燃料过多的生产</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-05/china-s-congress-pledges-to-fix-overproduction-of-steel-and-fuel</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国承诺解决过多的生产削弱其钢铁和石油部门，这是该国的两个表现最差，最受冲突的行业，因为政府希望重新配置其经济并实现强大的增长目标。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-05/china-s-congress-pledges-to-fix-overproduction-of-steel-and-fuel</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 05 Mar 2025 03:59:17 GMT</pubDate>
